      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This crystal ball is about 6 inches in diameter. While touching it, you can cast the scrying spell (save DC 17) with it.</p>\n<p>You can use an action to cast the detect thoughts spell (save DC 17) while you are scrying with the <em>crystal ball</em>, targeting creatures you can see within 30 feet of the spell’s sensor. You don't need to concentrate on this <em>detect thoughts</em> to maintain it during its duration, but it ends if scrying ends.</p>\n</div>",
